# HealthSync — Cursor Project Rules

## What This Project Is
HealthSync is a patient-first, longitudinal heart health intelligence system.
It detects meaningful physiological drift over time and generates natural language insights.

This is NOT:
- A diagnosis tool
- A medical replacement
- A generic AI chatbot
- An acute event detector (e.g. heart attack detection)

It IS:
- A personal baseline engine
- A trend + drift detection system
- An AI insight generator (narrative summaries from structured signals)
- Eventually: a full preventive health intelligence platform

